('92cb730c-8b4f-46ef-9925-4fab953694c6', 'ef49d218-b7e0-420c-a8b1-5c124d3a14cf', '275e5c3c-d565-4f5a-b832-4290cc6de915', '"he was the raf''s youngest pilot at the age of nineteen, barely escaped the wrath of an arms dealer in hamburg, got strafed by a mig during the nigerian civil war; the stasi arrested him, the israelis feted him, the ira threatened him. and that''s just for starters. forsyth has been writing extraordinary real-world novels of intrigue for over forty years-- but what most people don''t know is that some of his greatest stories of intrigue have been in his own life."', '720555427325a4103e612082cbc93c20', 't', 'f', 'f', 'f', 'f', '1708623782646'),
